<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>1244</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yǒu rén zài kuàng yě zǒu mí le lù, pí dài de shuǐ zǎo yǐ yòng jǐn.
 tā bǎ hái zi piē zài xiǎo shù dǐ xià, xiāng duì ér zuò fàng shēng dà kū.
 shén tīng jiàn le tóng zi de kū shēng, shén de shǐ zhě hū jiào xià jiǎ,
 bù yào hài pà bù yào hài pà, shén bì shǐ nǐ men chéng shòu de tǔ.
 zhǔ a, nǐ ài rú cǐ hào dà, měi yī gè líng hún nǐ dōu kàn gù.
 wǒ men yǒng yuǎn dōu shì nǐ de hái zi, xìn kào nǐ de rén shì hé děng yǒu fú.</lyrics>
<title>yǒu rén zài kuàng yě zǒu mí le lù 迦南1244</title>
</song>